{"id":964202261,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"3 weeks, 2 days","timestamp":1685950407,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"34 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/964202261/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Count of Integers","memory":"44.5 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    int mod=1000000007;\n    String s;\n    int min;\n    Integer[][][] dp;\n    int max;\n    public int count(String num1, String num2, int min_sum, int max_sum){\n        int sum=0;\n        dp=new Integer[23][2][401];\n        for(int i=0;i<num1.length();i++){\n            sum+=num1.charAt(i)-'0';\n        }\n        min=min_sum;\n        max=max_sum;\n        s=num1;\n        int one=rec(0,true,0);\n        s=num2;\n          dp=new Integer[23][2][401];\n        int two=rec(0,true,0);\n        if(sum>=min_sum && sum<=max_sum){\n            return (two-one+mod)%mod+1;\n        }\n        return (two-one+mod)%mod;\n\n\n    }\n    public int rec(int idx,boolean limit,int sum){\n        if(sum>max){\n            return 0;\n        }\n        if(idx==s.length()){\n            if(sum<=max && sum>=min){\n                return 1;\n            }\n            return 0;\n            \n        }\n        if(dp[idx][limit ? 1:0][sum]!=null){\n            return dp[idx][limit ? 1:0][sum];\n        }\n\n        int is=-1;\n        if(limit){\n         is= s.charAt(idx)-'0';\n        }\n        else{\n            is=9;\n        }\n        int ans=0;\n        for(int i=0;i<=is;i++){\n            ans=(ans+rec(idx+1,limit && (s.charAt(idx)-'0'==i),sum+i)%mod)%mod;\n        }\n        return dp[idx][limit ? 1:0][sum]=ans;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"count-of-integers","has_notes":false}
